M||titl|Promise.all() for Independent Operations
M||impa|ct
M||impa|2-10× improvement
M||tags|async, parallelization, promises, waterfalls
M||tx|---
M|Prom|tx|When async operations have no interdependencies, execute them concurrently using `Promise.all()`.
M|Prom|**In|**
M|Prom|tx|```ts
M|Prom|tx|const us = await fetchUser()
M|Prom|tx|const posts = await fetchPosts()
M|Prom|tx|const comments = await fetchComments()
M|Prom|tx|```
M|Prom|**Co|**
M|Prom|tx|```ts
M|Prom|tx|const [us, posts, comments] = await Promise.all([
M|Prom|tx|fetchUser(),
M|Prom|tx|fetchPosts(),
M|Prom|tx|fetchComments()
M|Prom|tx|])
M|Prom|tx|```